@host = http://localhost:8080

### 적립 - 기본
POST {{host}}/api/points/earn
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "1234567890",
  "amount": 500,
  "requestId": "http-req-1"
}

### 적립 -  동일 requestId → 중복 적립 없음
POST {{host}}/api/points/earn
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "1234567890",
  "amount": 500,
  "requestId": "http-req-1"
}

### 적립 - 만료일·수기 지급
POST {{host}}/api/points/earn
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "1111111111",
  "amount": 1000,
  "expireYmd": "20261231",
  "requestId": "http-req-2",
  "adminGrantedYn": "Y"
}

### 적립 - 다른 사용자
POST {{host}}/api/points/earn
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "9999999999",
  "amount": 300,
  "requestId": "http-req-3"
}

### 검증 실패 - amount 범위 밖 (400 예상)
POST {{host}}/api/points/earn
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "1234567890",
  "amount": 0,
  "requestId": "http-req-bad-1"
}

### 검증 실패 - userId 10자리 아님 (400 예상)
POST {{host}}/api/points/earn
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "12345",
  "amount": 100,
  "requestId": "http-req-bad-2"
}

### 검증 실패 - requestId 없음 (400 예상)
POST {{host}}/api/points/earn
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "1234567890",
  "amount": 100
}
